{"tid":2130823,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"被控以傘襲警 警長證供矛盾牽強 青年脫罪兼獲訟費","createTime":"2020-07-29T12:13:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-29T12:25:32.000Z","uid":39464,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"e89543b1dc53d1d70c555da585e45ceb476eef06","tid":2130823,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T12:13:20.000Z","msg":"去年7月14日市民在獲得不反對通知書下於沙田遊行示威，及後爆發警民衝突，大批警員衝入新城市廣場驅散示威者，有22歲青年被指用雨傘插警，被控襲警罪。惟案件經審訊後，裁判官李志豪今指警員證供前後不一，裁定被告罪名不成立兼得訟費。到庭支持的親友聞判即場鼓掌，更有人落淚。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200729/ZREZEC5BROJD2LVGYYL3VAVRZQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200729%2FZREZEC5BROJD2LVGYYL3VAVRZQ%2F&d=SjiHudolEFiOjT3rBZQy6YlFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=f2f9e5d6\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200729%2FZREZEC5BROJD2LVGYYL3VAVRZQ%2F&h=dc97a07f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200729/ZREZEC5BROJD2LVGYYL3VAVRZQ/</a>"},{"pid":"bf016214d671f34144438c6af1943031b18443c1","tid":2130823,"uid":156936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T12:14:22.000Z","msg":"我睇post都睇到落淚"},{"pid":"e841b610910ed4878d112ef900612a915b4e7287","tid":2130823,"uid":199893,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T12:14:44.000Z","msg":"恭喜手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62c46e85f72d84310005d4f0129dbd0eec7f94de","tid":2130823,"uid":267647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T12:15:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02e15cadf986453698fd0af694e59e356dc2f2c1","tid":2130823,"uid":309192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-29T12:16:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/n